<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>工作空间邀请</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
        }

        .title {
            color: #2d3748;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .invitation-info {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .info-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .accept-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #718096;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1 class="title">工作空间邀请</h1>
    </div>

    <p>您好！</p>

    <div class="content">
        <p><strong>{{inviterName}}</strong> 邀请您加入工作空间：</p>
        <div class="invitation-info">
            <div class="info-item"><strong>工作空间：</strong>{{workspaceName}}</div>
            <div class="info-item"><strong>邀请人：</strong>{{inviterName}}</div>
            <div class="info-item"><strong>有效期：</strong>{{expiryHours}} 小时</div>
        </div>

        <a href="{{invitationUrl}}" class="accept-button">接受邀请</a>
    </div>

    <p>如果您不认识邀请人或认为这是误发的邮件，请忽略此邮件。</p>

    <div class="footer">
        <p>此邮件由 Monie 系统自动发送</p>
        <p>需要帮助？请联系 supports@monie.cc</p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>